OL,3,CTrump tells ITV News Pope Leo must
OL,4,Cunderstand Iran cannot have a nuclear
OL,5,Cweapon
OL,7,FWords by US Correspondent Dan Rivers
OL,8,Fand Washington News Editor Jonathan
OL,9,FWald
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV News, President Trump
OL,12,Fsaid that "the Pope has to understand
OL,13,Fthat Iran cannot have a nuclear
OL,14,Fweapon."
OL,16,FIn the midst of an escalating public
OL,17,Fspat between the Pope and the
OL,18,FPresident, Dan Rivers asked Trump
OL,19,Fwhether he felt the Pope was being
OL,20,Fdisrespectful to him.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
