OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1776387789
OL,3,CTrump tells ITV News Pope Leo must
OL,4,Cunderstand Iran cannot have a nuclear
OL,5,Cweapon
OL,7,F"I don't think about it like that,"
OL,8,FTrump replied. "The Pope has to
OL,9,Funderstand that Iran cannot have a
OL,10,Fnuclear weapon and the Pope has to
OL,11,Funderstand that you can't let a
OL,12,Fcountry kill 42,000 protesters who are
OL,13,Ftotally unarmed protesting. You can't
OL,14,Fdo that.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
