OL,3,CTrump tells ITV News Pope Leo must
OL,4,Cunderstand Iran cannot have a nuclear
OL,5,Cweapon
OL,7,FSo the Pope, you know I know his
OL,8,Fbrother, his brother is MAGA all the
OL,9,Fway, you know that Louis is a great
OL,10,Fguy but ... you cannot let Iran have a
OL,11,Fnuclear weapon or the entire world
OL,12,Fcould be gone and you know when the
OL,13,FPope realises that I think we'll have
OL,14,Fa different understanding."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
