OL,3,CTrump tells ITV News Pope Leo must
OL,4,Cunderstand Iran cannot have a nuclear
OL,5,Cweapon
OL,7,FIn a worsening war of words between
OL,8,Fthe US President and the pontiff, Pope
OL,9,FLeo XIV used a speech in Cameroon on
OL,10,FThursday to say that the world is
OL,11,Fbeing "ravaged by a handful of
OL,12,Ftyrants" who spend billions on war, in
OL,13,Fcomments that have been widely
OL,14,Finterpreted as a critique of Trump.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
