OL,3,CTrump tells ITV News Pope Leo must
OL,4,Cunderstand Iran cannot have a nuclear
OL,5,Cweapon
OL,7,FThis past Sunday, Trump posted on
OL,8,FTruth Social that the Pope was "WEAK
OL,9,Fon crime" and "terrible for foreign
OL,10,Fpolicy", claiming that the first US-
OL,11,Fborn pontiff would not have been
OL,12,Fchosen to lead the Catholic Church had
OL,13,Fit not been for Trump.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
