OL,3,CTrump tells ITV News Pope Leo must
OL,4,Cunderstand Iran cannot have a nuclear
OL,5,Cweapon
OL,7,FThe following morning, Leo responded
OL,8,Fon board the papal plane, during a
OL,9,Ftrip to Algeria, saying on camera to
OL,10,Fjournalists, "I have no fear of the
OL,11,FTrump administration, or speaking out
OL,12,Floudly of the message of the Gospel,
OL,13,Fwhich is what I believe I am here to
OL,14,Fdo."
OL,16,FWhen asked if he would be prepared to
OL,17,Fmeet with Pope Leo to settle their
OL,18,Fdifferences, Trump said he didn't
OL,19,Fthink it was necessary.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
